OL,3,CParasite outbreak in Brixham cost
OL,4,CSouth West Water nearly #40m
OL,6,FThis is up from around #20 million in
OL,7,Fcosts in the first half of its year,
OL,8,Fwhen it revealed more than #16 million
OL,9,Fwas paid out for the Brixham issue
OL,10,Fafter compensating affected customers,
OL,11,Ftogether with a further #4 million for
OL,12,Fits overhaul programme.
OL,14,FDespite the rising financial toll, the
OL,15,Fgroup said on Monday 31 March that its
OL,16,Funderlying earnings would be "broadly
OL,17,Fflat" compared with the first half and
OL,18,Fthat it was on track with its own
OL,19,Fexpectations for the full year
OL,20,Ffinancial year.
