OL,3,CParasite outbreak in Brixham cost
OL,4,CSouth West Water nearly #40m
OL,6,FThe outbreak in May 2024 left some
OL,7,Fpeople in hospital and hundreds of
OL,8,Fothers ill after contamination of the
OL,9,Fwater supply by cryptosporidium, a
OL,10,Fparasite which causes sickness and
OL,11,Fdiarrhoea.
OL,13,FAround 17,000 households and
OL,14,Fbusinesses in the Brixham area were
OL,15,Fissued with a "boil water" notice as
OL,16,Fscores of reported cases emerged.
