OL,6,FThe notice, instructing them not to
OL,7,Fuse tap water for drinking without
OL,8,Fboiling and cooling it first, remained
OL,9,Fin place for eight weeks for some
OL,10,Fhouseholds.
OL,12,FIn a Commons committee session in
OL,13,FFebruary, Pennon chief executive Susan
OL,14,FDavy apologised to customers over
OL,15,Fpollution incidents, including the
OL,16,F"devastating" Devon case, while also
OL,17,Frevealing her salary has risen this
OL,18,Fyear.
