OL,3,CParasite outbreak in Brixham cost
OL,4,CSouth West Water nearly #40m
OL,6,FMs Davy has faced criticism after it
OL,7,Fwas revealed that her pay package
OL,8,Fjumped 58% to #860,000.
OL,10,FShe also told the MPs in the committee
OL,11,Fsession that her base salary is rising
OL,12,Ffrom #494,000 to #511,000 this year.
OL,14,FSouth West Water customers will see
OL,15,Ftheir bills increase by 23% over the
OL,16,Fcoming five years, helping the company
OL,17,Fpay for improvements to its
OL,18,Finfrastructure and reduce pollution
OL,19,Fincidents.
