OL,3,CParasite outbreak in Brixham cost
OL,4,CSouth West Water nearly #40m
OL,6,FThe costs of the parasitic water
OL,7,Foutbreak saw Pennon report widened
OL,8,Fbottom line pre-tax losses of #38.8
OL,9,Fmillion in the six months to
OL,10,FSeptember, against losses of #34
OL,11,Fmillion a year earlier.
OL,13,FThe company spent about #4 million on
OL,14,Frestructuring the business in the
OL,15,Ffirst half alone, having also bought
OL,16,FSutton and East Surrey (SES) Water for
OL,17,F#350 million.
OL,19,FIt is looking to cut costs across SES,
OL,20,Fwhich was also loss-making in the
OL,21,Ffirst half.
